    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but they're constantly seeing me struggle. every time i mess up or get overwhelmed, it just drags them down too. it feels like my presence is just this constant weight in the house. i look at them and i just think... if i wasn't around, they could actually breathe. they wouldn't have to worry about me anymore.",
